/* Common Maxima checks for the PG-II electronics practicals. */
kill(all)$
/* Zener / MOSFET sample calculations */
Vz:5.1$ Vin:9$ Rs:470$ IL:0.003$
Is:(Vin-Vz)/Rs$ Iz:Is-IL$ [Is,Iz]$ float([Is,Iz]);
Vt:1.9$ K:0.8$ Vgs:3.0$
Id:K*(Vgs-Vt)^2$ float(Id);
/* Hartley oscillator */
L1:10e-6$ L2:20e-6$ M:2e-6$ C:4.7e-9$
f:1/(2*%pi*sqrt((L1+L2+2*M)*C))$ float(f);
/* ADC step size and quantisation bound */
Vref:5$ n:8$ q:Vref/2^n$ [q,q/2]$ float([q,q/2]);
